    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "route_index_content",
      "x": 70,
      "y": 222,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 250,
      "text": "Component: EntitiesIndexPage\nArchetype: <Page archetype=\"overview\">\n\nEndpoints:\n  GET /api/relationship/entities\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/queue\n\nUI features:\n  Tabular list (EntityMark glyph +\n  canonical_name + tier + last_seen)\n  Filter chips (type, has=contact,\n  stale, unidentified)\n  Curation queue right rail\n  Cmd-K affordance (⌘K)\n\nRedirects:\n  /contacts → /entities?has=contact\n\nFact contributors:\n  relationship.entity_facts\n  (has-email, has-phone, has-handle,\n  has-address predicates)",
      "originalText": "Component: EntitiesIndexPage\nArchetype: <Page archetype=\"overview\">\n\nEndpoints:\n  GET /api/relationship/entities\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/queue\n\nUI features:\n  Tabular list (EntityMark glyph +\n  canonical_name + tier + last_seen)\n  Filter chips (type, has=contact,\n  stale, unidentified)\n  Curation queue right rail\n  Cmd-K affordance (⌘K)\n\nRedirects:\n  /contacts → /entities?has=contact\n\nFact contributors:\n  relationship.entity_facts\n  (has-email, has-phone, has-handle,\n  has-address predicates)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
