    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "route_columns_content",
      "x": 770,
      "y": 222,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 180,
      "text": "Component: ColumnsPage (EntityFinder)\nArchetype: <Page archetype=\"overview\">\n\nQuery: ?path=<csv of entity_ids>\n  Col-0 defaults to owner entity\n\nEndpoints (client-side chaining):\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/{id}/neighbours\n  (no dedicated server endpoint needed)\n\nFact contributors:\n  relationship: all relational\n  predicates (grouped by predicate)",
      "originalText": "Component: ColumnsPage (EntityFinder)\nArchetype: <Page archetype=\"overview\">\n\nQuery: ?path=<csv of entity_ids>\n  Col-0 defaults to owner entity\n\nEndpoints (client-side chaining):\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/{id}/neighbours\n  (no dedicated server endpoint needed)\n\nFact contributors:\n  relationship: all relational\n  predicates (grouped by predicate)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
