    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "route_socialmap_content",
      "x": 430,
      "y": 532,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 180,
      "text": "Component: SocialMapView (refactored)\nArchetype: <Page archetype=\"overview\">\n\nPreserved unchanged from prior spec;\nUI behaviour identical pre/post refactor.\nRefactored: SocialMapPage →\n  SocialMapView (for SubpageTabs chrome)\n\nEndpoints:\n  GET /api/relationship/dunbar/ranking\n\nFact contributors:\n  dunbar_tier_override triples\n  (relationship)",
      "originalText": "Component: SocialMapView (refactored)\nArchetype: <Page archetype=\"overview\">\n\nPreserved unchanged from prior spec;\nUI behaviour identical pre/post refactor.\nRefactored: SocialMapPage →\n  SocialMapView (for SubpageTabs chrome)\n\nEndpoints:\n  GET /api/relationship/dunbar/ranking\n\nFact contributors:\n  dunbar_tier_override triples\n  (relationship)",
