    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "editorial_content",
      "x": 70,
      "y": 812,
      "width": 480,
      "height": 330,
      "text": "Component: EntityDetailPage\nArchetype: <Page archetype=\"detail\">\nHeadline: Display 44px (canonical_name)\nMode persists: localStorage[entities.detail.mode]\n\nEndpoints:\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/{id}\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/{id}/contacts\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/{id}/timeline\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/{id}/notes\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/{id}/interactions\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/{id}/gifts\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/{id}/loans\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/{id}/activity\n\nFact contributors by module:\n  relationship: contact_note, gift, loan,\n    interaction_*, life_event,\n    dunbar_tier_override\n  chronicler: chronicles (interaction facts\n    from passive sync)\n  calendar: interaction_* (meeting events)\n\nUI: unified ActivityTimeline with\n  filter pills (All|Interactions|Notes|\n  Gifts|Loans|Life events)\n  Gifts panel + Loans panel\n  Voice gloss (Source Serif 4 italic 16px)\n  Forget affordance in Page header\n  Link → /entities/:id (memory view)",
      "originalText": "Component: EntityDetailPage\nArchetype: <Page archetype=\"detail\">\nHeadline: Display 44px (canonical_name)\nMode persists: localStorage[entities.detail.mode]\n\nEndpoints:\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/{id}\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/{id}/contacts\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/{id}/timeline\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/{id}/notes\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/{id}/interactions\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/{id}/gifts\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/{id}/loans\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/{id}/activity\n\nFact contributors by module:\n  relationship: contact_note, gift, loan,\n    interaction_*, life_event,\n    dunbar_tier_override\n  chronicler: chronicles (interaction facts\n    from passive sync)\n  calendar: interaction_* (meeting events)\n\nUI: unified ActivityTimeline with\n  filter pills (All|Interactions|Notes|\n  Gifts|Loans|Life events)\n  Gifts panel + Loans panel\n  Voice gloss (Source Serif 4 italic 16px)\n  Forget affordance in Page header\n  Link → /entities/:id (memory view)",
      "fontSize": 11,
