    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "workbench_content",
      "x": 590,
      "y": 812,
      "width": 480,
      "height": 330,
      "text": "Component: EntityDetailPage (mode=workbench)\nArchetype: <Page archetype=\"overview\">\nHeadline: text-2xl H1 (44px Display forbidden)\nToggle: icon button in Page actions slot\n\nSame endpoints as Editorial mode\nPlus:\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/{id}/facts\n    (ProvenanceGrid, bu-mg4dk)\n\nUI differences from Editorial:\n  ActivityTimeline → ProvenanceGrid\n  ProvenanceGrid: dense, sortable\n    columns (conf, src, last_seen,\n    weight, verified, primary)\n  Contacts as predicate+value+provenance\n    grid (not grouped visually)\n  All provenance metadata surfaced\n\nMode toggle key:\n  localStorage[entities.detail.mode]\n  (distinct from butlers.detail.mode)\n\n?mode=workbench overrides localStorage\nfor current page load only",
      "originalText": "Component: EntityDetailPage (mode=workbench)\nArchetype: <Page archetype=\"overview\">\nHeadline: text-2xl H1 (44px Display forbidden)\nToggle: icon button in Page actions slot\n\nSame endpoints as Editorial mode\nPlus:\n  GET /api/relationship/entities/{id}/facts\n    (ProvenanceGrid, bu-mg4dk)\n\nUI differences from Editorial:\n  ActivityTimeline → ProvenanceGrid\n  ProvenanceGrid: dense, sortable\n    columns (conf, src, last_seen,\n    weight, verified, primary)\n  Contacts as predicate+value+provenance\n    grid (not grouped visually)\n  All provenance metadata surfaced\n\nMode toggle key:\n  localStorage[entities.detail.mode]\n  (distinct from butlers.detail.mode)\n\n?mode=workbench overrides localStorage\nfor current page load only",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
